data.description: Discover single-level luxury in Layton's Glenhawk Subdivision. This exquisite 3-bed, 2-bath home showcases new hardwood floors, a spacious great room, and an oversized master suite for ultimate comfort. With easy access to Grey Hawk Park and nearby schools, your dream lifestyle is within reach. Qualified buyers can seize the exceptional VA assumable option at a low 2.25% interest rate. Don't wait; your dream home awaits! Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records .
